Please see lazy foo tuturials number 1 and 3 to install SDL
	tutorial 1: http://lazyfoo.net/SDL_tutorials/lesson01/index.php
	tutorial 3: http://lazyfoo.net/SDL_tutorials/lesson03/index.php

The file screen_paramaters.h controls the size of the screen and the x and y ranges of the plotting region.
	
To change the potential edit part::energy and part::accel part.cpp.

